  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">The data collected via these cookies is anonymous and the information is not linked to your personally identifiable information without your permission. The "persistent" cookies placed by our third party ad servers will remain on your computer after you have left our site for up to 20 years unless you choose to delete them.</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

